В роли главной героини снялась знаменитая белорусская модель Наталья Макей.

description:
Yo! This is another upload for all the real Wu-Tang/RZA fans! :)
It's the full soundtrack score album from the movie "Ghost Dog: The Way Of The Samurai" 
by The RZA! It's the japan import version, released in 1999!

There are 2 Versions of the soundtrack: 
The first one is an album with Hip-Hop tracks (all produced by RZA) that mostly do not 
appear in the movie. The artists on the album are all affiliates from the Wu-Tang family 
plus some other well-known MCs like Kool G Rap, Jeru The Damaja and more. 
Only a few songs from the soundtrack can be heard in the movie.

The second version was only released in Japan! So its very expensive and also hard to find. 
It features all the RZA-produced Instrumentals that are used in the movie! 
Also, there are some bonus beats and songs from the Wu-Tang Clan and RZA himself! 
In this video you can listen to the full RZA-produced soundtrack score from the japanese 
version of the album! Enjoy!!!!
title: Ghost Dog: The Way Of The Samurai (OST) by The RZA (Japan Import Version) [FULL ALBUM]
